The paper discusses network virtualization and proposes a new algorithm for solving the virtual path embedding problem. This topic falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The paper also mentions energy efficiency, which could fall under the category of systems and control (cs.SI) or computer engineering (cs.CE). Additionally, the paper discusses Service Level Objectives (SLOs), which could fall under the category of information theory (cs.IT).
